  <description>
    <p>Vulnerabilities have been discovered in the packages listed below.
      Please review the CVE identifiers in the Reference section for details.
    </p>
    
    <ul>
      <li>FMOD Studio</li>
      <li>PEAR Mail</li>
      <li>LVM2</li>
      <li>GnuCash</li>
      <li>xine-lib</li>
      <li>Last.fm Scrobbler</li>
      <li>WebKitGTK+</li>
      <li>shadow tool suite</li>
      <li>PEAR</li>
      <li>unixODBC</li>
